Product Description

MelodySusie Electric Portable Nail Drill

Multifunctional Nail Drill for You!

The MelodySusie portable nail drill is an all-in-one nail maintenance device that allows you to “bring your beauty salon home” and do your own manicures. Functional, versatile, and easy-to-use, it's an essential tool for nail-care veterans and newcomers alike.

What’re its key Features?

  • 1) 0-20,000 RPM continuously alterable speed switching, works great for polishing, removing your acrylic nails or gel nails.
  • 2) Low heat, low noise, low vibration, and portable compact, easy to use this nail drill machine
  • 3) Easy to operate with Forward/Reverse directions, suitable for left-hand and right-hand.
  • 4) USB charging design lets you get cord freedom, feel free to enjoy your nail art at home or travel.
  • 5) Compact and lightweight design make it easy to carry.

Before Purchase Please Note:

  • 1) It is not a rechargeable nail drill, which needs to be charged while working. The USB charging cord enables you to use the machine anywhere you need.
  • 2) The package doesn't come with the adapter. It is recommended to use 5V/2A adapter, please don't use the adapter that exceeds 5V/2A.

High Powerful Nail Drill

  • Built of a high-quality powerful motor and comfortable handheld design, super easy use for all level technicians and newcomers.
  • Full set nail drill attachments for all-around grinding, carving, cutting, polishing, and removing acrylic and poly gel nails; also work well for cuticle and dead skin cleaning.

Efficient Heat Dissipation

  • The body of this efile is built of aluminum alloy, which can contribute to heat dissipation and long-time working.
  • Note: No more than 20 minutes of continuous use each time is recommended.

Low Noise & Low Vibration

  • This electric nail file is built of a powerful yet quiet motor with smart heat dissipation, keep this machine quiet and stable when you do the manicures.
  • It is exact enough for nail polishing work and low vibration. You deserve a professional nail drill for your nail artwork.

USB Charging Cord

  • Comes with an upgrade USB interface cord, it is easy for you to use it with any USB socket. No more worry about the adapter cord limited, feel free to enjoy your nail art at home or travel.
  • Note: The package doesn't include the adapter. It is recommended to use 5V 2A adapter, please don't use the adapter that exceeds 5V/2A.

Interchangeable Bits & Sanding Bands

  • 11 Kinds of 3/32” Nail Drill Bits: For all-round grinding, carving, cutting, polishing, removing for cuticle, acrylic nails, and gel nails.
  • High Quality Sanding Bands: Comes with 56pcs Sanding Bands, suitable for various needs
  • Nail Dust Brush: Made in soft nylon with mushroom-shaped head and smooth handle decorated by tiny rhinestone for easier hold.

For basic use, follow these simple steps

Step 1: Plug in your chosen drill bit.

Step 2: Connect the power cord with nail drill handpiece and the other end with the wall socket.

Step 3: Control the Forward/ OFF / Reverse button in the middle of the cord to turn on/off or change the rotation direction.

Step 4: Control the SPEED SWITCH in the middle of the cord to adjust speed.

What you will get

  • 1 x Nail Drill
  • 1 x 11pcs Nail Drill Bits
  • 1 x 56pcs Sanding Band
  • 1 x Nail Dust Brush
  • 1 x USB Cord

Specifications

  • Bits Size: 3/32 Inch
  • Input Voltage Range: 100-240V, 0/60Hz, 5V 2A (US Plug)
  • Output Voltage: DC 0-12V
  • Handpiece Length: 5.1 inches
  • Handpiece Weight: 2.2 ounces

WARM TIPS:

1. This nail drill is designed for acrylic gel nails. So if you want to remove the gel polish of natural nails but you are not a professional manicurist, please use the nail polish remover pads instead of a nail drill to avoid damage to the nail bed.

2. In order to meet the requirements of professional manicurists, this product is designed to have an adjustable rotation speed of 0-20000 rpm. Please slowly adjust it from a low speed to a higher speed that you like when you are using it. Do not adjust it to the highest speed all at once to prevent the improper operation from hurting your nails.

3. A high-speed motor will inevitably generate heat, so please do not use the nail drill for too long each time. When you feel that the nail drill is overheated, please stop using it immediately and wait for the heat to dissipate before using it again. (no more than 20 minutes of continuous use each time is recommended)

4. Please use the adapter in the original package. When the nail drill is rotating, please turn off the switch before replacing the nail drill bit.

5. Please do not pull the power cord or let the device drop or by other impacts.

6. Please do not use the device when the connecting wires broke and do not touch the plug with a wet hand to prevent electric leakage and shock or fire. Do not operate in wet or moist conditions/Only a dry cloth is allowed for cleaning.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
